Acceptance Test

Timer is not displayed -- Unacceptable
Timer is displayed 
Timer starts at 0 and counts seconds
Timer increases  -- Acceptable
Timer decreases -- Unacceptable
Timer does not count seconds
  -- Unacceptable
Timer does not start at 0 
-- Unacceptable


Functional Requirement
-System starts a timer in the beginning of the game

Expected Results

As the game starts, the timer should be visible to the user and should start counting each second from 0
Once the game is quit the timer should stop and be used for scoring
As the next game starts, the timer should once again start from 0 and count each second upwards
